{title: Low Light}
{artist: Pearl Jam}
{meta: type Chords}

Email: antonuccichristopher@yahoo.com

This is one of the best Pearl Jam songs...EVER! An underrated classic as well. I decided to
add the chords and some tabs in this, especially the solo. This is my first time by the way
so bear with me. I had my music teacher write down the chords and the other parts I mention.


